OL,3,C'Hike hat-trick' hits energy customers
OL,5,FBrace for the third successive energy
OL,6,Fprice cap increase since autumn, as 22
OL,7,Fmillion homes face a rise of #111 a
OL,8,Fyear.
OL,10,FIt's being called the "hat-trick
OL,11,Fhike", three energy price rises, one
OL,12,Fafter another, since last autumn.
OL,13,FThey've tightened around customers
OL,14,Ffinances like a ratchet.
