OL,3,C'Hike hat-trick' hits energy customers
OL,5,FITV News' Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,6,Fshares his advice for those struggling
OL,7,Fwith rising energy bills
OL,9,FThis news has been heart sinking and
OL,10,Ffinance sinking for many. Millions are
OL,11,Falready in energy debt and even though
OL,12,Faverage wages have risen, so too have
OL,13,Fessentials.
OL,15,FAs the energy increases arrive in
OL,16,FApril, so do water bill rises
OL,17,Faveraging #123 more each year. Food
OL,18,Fcosts are still one of the biggest
OL,19,Ffactors in rising inflation and now we
OL,20,Fget this energy bill rise for millions
OL,21,Fof customers.
